            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">18/8/59. ¶ My dear Mr Hyndman ¶  ¶ It will give me much pleasure, if you will take tea with me on Saturday night, when we can enjoy a talk about your trip to the East, and when I will be glad to show ...</supplied>
